## Demo - Users and Perms 

Create user called Tom 
Generate certificates for Tom 
Getting it signed by k8s ca 
Create client key for Tom using openSSL 
Create CertificateSigningRequest for key 
Approve CertificateSigningRequest
Get signed certificate
Provide Tom with signed certificate
Allow Tom to access the cluster using his own certificate
Set permissions for Tom user 
Give permissions to create, delete, update k8s resources 
Validate user permissions 


Create non human user for ci/cd tool to access cluster with own users
Create service account for Jenkins 
Give permissions to create, delete, update k8s resources 
